Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天啊 这一刻终于到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God. This is it. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:12.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望是你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I hope it's you.
