Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}首先 我非常爱你们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}First of all, I love you both so much.
