Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们都可以当伴娘 没有人会难过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We all get to do it and no one gets upset.
