Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然我们会帮你决定 我们会尽力帮你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Of course we'll help you decide. We'll do anything we can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:08.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想要举杯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'd like to make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}敬未来的钱德宾太太…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To the future Mrs. Chandler Bing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:15.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我最好的朋友跟最棒的…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...my best friend and truly one of the nicest people that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我真的还没有决定   - 好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Really not deciding.     - Fine.
