Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在胡说什么？混蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What are you talking about, bitch?
