Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 为什么这件事这么重要？ - 那你为什么觉得这么重要呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Why does it even matter?     - Why does it matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为她马上就要结婚了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because this one is now.
