Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:53.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不为什么 我只是说…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No reason. I'm just saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会在那里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...that's where I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然结局不如预期中理想 事实上我很满意自己的表现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As bad as that went, I actually enjoyed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:24.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想我要为我做过的 所有蠢事道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think that I'm going to apologize for all the stupid things that I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:27.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你为什么不改掉 做蠢事的习惯？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why don't you just stop doing stupid things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那样子你就不必道歉了   - 我希望可以两件事一起做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Then you wouldn't have to apologize.     - I'd love it if I could do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 我得问你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right, I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我变胖了 你会跟我分手吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Will you break up with me if I get fat again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:47.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你跟茱丽分手 她变得有多胖呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You broke up with Julie. How much weight did she gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:50.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她胖了一百四十五磅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A hundred and forty-five pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在一年之内？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In one year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天啊 她吃了什么？ 她的家人吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}My God, what did she eat? Her family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那不是重点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道那样跟别人分手太蠢了 但当时我才十五岁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I know it was a stupid reason to break up with someone, but I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对 不只十五岁的男孩 觉得肥胖是个问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah, well, that's not the only time this was an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你还记得 你跟我们一起过感恩节的事吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You remember when you spent Thanksgiving with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你骂我胖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You called me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等一下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那完全是另一回事   - 怎么说？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- That was totally different.     - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:22.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不该听到那句话 我是在你背后偷偷说的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You were not supposed to hear that. I said that behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我怀孕了呢？ 我会变得跟现在不一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What if I have babies, okay? I'm gonna look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以接受那样的事 但我不相信你能做到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm okay with that, but I'm not sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:33.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你得了解我不认为 你是个苗条的大美女\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have to realize I don't think of you as a thin, beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我待会儿就会为这种事情道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is one of the things that I can apologize for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是说你是摩妮卡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What I mean is, you're Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我吗？我爱上的人是摩妮卡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay? And I am in love with Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}继续说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不论你变胖或是变瘦…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So you can balloon up or you can shrink down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还是会爱你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and I will still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:02.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使我缩小到只有两寸高？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even if I shrink down to 2 inches tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那我会把你放在我的口袋里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'd carry you around in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我爱你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}备胎还是对女人很有一套\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Skidmark still got a way with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗨 菲比\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hi, Pheebs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嗨   - 嗨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Hi.     - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我来跟你道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I just want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我真的很抱歉我太孩子气了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm really sorry I was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:27.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那太可笑了 瑞秋 我们都曾经是小孩子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's ridiculous. Rachel, we were all babies once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.15,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你是说今天的事   - 没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Oh, you mean today.     - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:37.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对 你知道吗？ 你应该赢的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah, and you know, you deserve to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我一直在想这件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I was thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果你是摩妮卡的伴娘 那我就是你的伴娘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you're Monica's maid of honor, I get to be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 没错   - 对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Oh, yeah.     - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:50.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摩妮卡跟钱德订婚时 我收集了一些东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When Monica and Chandler got engaged, I put some stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 以防万一   - 那真的是太好了 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Just in case.     - Oh, that's so sweet. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:57.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道摩妮卡 很喜欢这本诗集\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Here is a book of poetry that I know Monica loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天啊 这真有趣 你看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, God, this is funny. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:03.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是有一年万圣节 她打扮成新娘的照片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Here's a picture from one Halloween when she dressed up as a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她要我帮她拉婚纱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}She made me carry her train...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那真的很奇怪 因为我扮的是神力女超人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...which was weird because I was Wonder Woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:13.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喔 这是我发现的小包包\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, and here's a little purse that I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想应该可以把婚戒放在这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I just thought they could hold the rings in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 喔   - 还有…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Oh.     - Something. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:23.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}上好的手帕 因为很多人会在婚礼哭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...vintage handkerchiefs, you know, because people cry at weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.49,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得拿几条走\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm just gonna grab a couple of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这真的是棒极了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This stuff is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我都忘了我把它放在这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I forgot this was in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我留下来 要在自己婚礼上用的吊袜带\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This was the garter that I was saving for my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:42.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望它能成为 被摩妮卡"借走的东西"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I wanted it to be Monica's "something borrowed."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它还是蓝色的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And it's blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.81,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}瑞秋 我认为你应该 当摩妮卡的伴娘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Rach, I think that you should be Monica's maid of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 为什么？ - 因为我想这对你来说意义更重大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Why?     - Because I think it means more to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但菲比 你赢了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But, Pheebs, honey, you earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没关系 我是说…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's fine. I mean, this is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:11.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你从十四岁就想这么做了吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...that you've been thinking about since you were, what, 14?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.50,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 那时我才十岁 我发育的很早\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, I was 10. I just developed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Man alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿 怎么了？ - 嘿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Hey, what's going on?     - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们决定由瑞秋来当你的伴娘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We decided Rachel is going to be your maid of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那真的是太棒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:31.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哇 太棒了 我们得开始计划了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, wow. Okay, we really have to start planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.64,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有很多特别的好点子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I have really specific ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们应该一星期开四次会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We should meet four times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到我家来 我们得在上班前开会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come to my place, we'll get together before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:43.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你觉得如何？六点半 我家见 好兴奋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What do you say, 6:30, my place? So excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 你现在笑吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah, okay. You laugh now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她就会是你的伴娘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}She's gonna be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我睡得好熟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Great nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:15.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.45,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老兄 你在做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Dude, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}失陪了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Excuse me.
